{"tid":760774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[左膠女權失蹤] 中國封殺#MeToo 學者：為鞏固政權","createTime":"2018-07-30T00:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:41:12.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a006983c0daace2a64ec8ca1e1c24e1d31111840","tid":760774,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:05:10.000Z","msg":"中國封殺#MeToo 學者：為鞏固政權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3279105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3279105&d=JOglu5YfauMX5Jo8bnbi2gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7fe09fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3279105</a><br />\n<br />\n中國#Me Too運動在網路上激烈展開，卻在日前遭到中國官方嚴厲封殺！根據《紐約時報》報導，中國政府自本周開始刪除部分對性侵陳述的公開信件，《Quartz》也報導，許多大陸的微博用戶發現他們無法發布或搜尋#Metoo標籤，而相關頁面皆顯示，「該主題根據相關法律和政策不存在。」加州柏克萊大學教授蕭強表示，任何會影響中共政權穩定性的輿論，都會透過網路審查進行屏蔽。<br />\n<br />\n《[紐約時報(<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/26/world/asia/china-metoo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchina-metoo.html&d=JOglu5YfauMX5Jo8bnbi2gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ee326aa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/26/world/asia/china-metoo.html</a>)]》指出，自上周四，新聞主播朱軍性侵指控的公開信批露後，大量以#Metoo為標籤的言論陸續出現在大陸社交媒體網站，並引起巨大迴響。但原先倡導性別平等的中國政府，卻因為一些官員對#Metoo在歐美所帶來的影響而感到不安，而將其視為顛覆力量。而為了使社會回歸穩定，中國政府決定安排審查，限制#Metoo運動的傳播，不僅禁止使用#Metoo標籤，更刪除了相關信件。<br />\n<br />\n美國數位財經新聞媒體報導。《[Quartz(<a href=\"https://qz.com/1265510/china-tried-to-crush-metoo-but-its-making-a-comeback/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2F1265510%2Fchina-tried-to-crush-metoo-but-its-making-a-comeback%2F&d=JOglu5YfauMX5Jo8bnbi2gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d4747ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qz.com/1265510/china-tried-to-crush-metoo-but-its-making-a-comeback/</a>)]》，控訴朱軍性侵的被害人表示，自己曾在案發當時受到警察恐嚇，要他不要污衊央視主持人朱軍的名聲。而當指控的公開信公開後，審查機構迅速將#Metoo的主題標籤從熱門話題中撤下，並禁止民眾使用相關標籤，搜尋相關資訊，則會顯示「該主題根據相關法律和政策不存在。」<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》援引香港大學教授傅景華表示，官員們可能會擔心#Metoo運動將許多人團結起來，並將矛頭指向企業、大學或政府，這樣的群眾動員是中國官方司所不樂見的。曾任中國人權總部執行主任的蕭強也指出，此次#Metoo運動中國政府屏蔽眾多女權主義者的論述，也刪除許多揭發信件，為的就是抑制運動規模擴大後，損及中共執政合法性的各種可能。"},{"pid":"2a2a094ab8558e5a49231a533f71e73975aea38a","tid":760774,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:06:13.000Z","msg":"黑社會大戰黑社會"},{"pid":"906ad28f7e8b285ad53ce636c5489eedcb42f1ff","tid":760774,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd098e19d3e837fba79f66a42262d3b6638b0c13","tid":760774,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"更加突出疫苗問題不可站邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55e6cfd46a9d729d6487d37ae9f4849f969e2ea","tid":760774,"uid":172893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"鬼打鬼"},{"pid":"6d992e0d007256a98150e126a847cb0f9140005c","tid":760774,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd098e19d3e837fba79f66a42262d3b6638b0c13","tid":760774,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"更加突出疫苗問題不可站邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"BTW 大陸會將件事推向令一個極端<br />\n<br />\n以後有咩大事　女人會變共敵　替死鬼一定係女人　用翻古代女人禍國果套　Ｄ人就會接受到"},{"pid":"1cd253fa98ffdd59dc0b036ff5bf21c34d6e3cef","tid":760774,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d992e0d007256a98150e126a847cb0f9140005c","tid":760774,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c